cc:Work.dc:title: Openclipart Worldnews Brings Your News in Clipart
cc:Work.dc:description: Today we launched Openclipart Worldnews which brings your news topics in clipart. Any artists may create clipart for relevant worldnews topics simply by uploading clipart from the main page of the Openclipart website, or tagging pre-existing clipart with the tag "worldnews." 2014
